ğŸ”§ Troubleshooting
Issue	Fix
"Permission denied"	Run chmod +x filename.sh
No .sh option	Use nano or right-click â†’ "Create Document" â†’ "Empty File"
Windows line endings	Run sudo apt install dos2unix then dos2unix file.sh
